-- site-doc.header: Properties:

Below are details of all properties of `-- ds.hero-cover` component.

-- site-doc.component-property: `title`
type: Caption (`required`)

This is a default property of the `hero` component. It’s used to add a
title to `hero` component.

-- site-doc.component-property: `body`
type: Caption (`required`)

This is a default property of the `hero` component. It’s used to add a
body to `hero` component.

-- site-doc.component-property: `hero-image`
type: ftd.image-src (`required`)

This is a default property of the `hero` component. Using `hero-image`
attribute image can be added.

-- site-doc.component-property: `cta-primary`
type: String (`optional`)

This is a default property of the `hero` component. It’s used to add a
click to action button title.

-- site-doc.component-property: `cta-primary-link`
type: String (`Default`)

This is a default property of the `hero` component. It’s used to add a
link to click to action button.

-- site-doc.component-property: `cta-primary-icon`
type: String (`Default`)

This is a default property of the `hero` component. It’s used to add a
icon in the button.

-- site-doc.component-property: `cta-secondary`
